116
00:14:25,228 --> 00:14:26,228
Carlita.

117
00:14:28,312 --> 00:14:30,395
Did you do that drawing outside, Carlita?

118
00:14:30,978 --> 00:14:34,062
The one where the girl's floating
above the other girls?

119
00:14:36,603 --> 00:14:38,187
I thought it was very nice.

120
00:14:48,562 --> 00:14:49,603
Thank you.

121
00:14:51,645 --> 00:14:52,645
Come.

122
00:14:59,895 --> 00:15:02,103
