139
00:17:22,311 --> 00:17:24,061
Then you must tie her to the bed.

140
00:17:25,436 --> 00:17:28,061
Here. Let me show you.

141
00:18:06,478 --> 00:18:07,478
Hi.

142
00:18:10,645 --> 00:18:11,937
You must be Margaretta.

143
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:13,353
Yes.

144
00:18:13,770 --> 00:18:14,770
I'm Luz.

145
00:18:16,770 --> 00:18:17,770
Did I wake you?

146
00:18:17,937 --> 00:18:18,937
No, no.

147
00:18:20,228 --> 00:18:21,353
I was having a nightmare.

148
00:18:22,520 --> 00:18:23,895
First night nerves?

149
00:18:24,062 --> 00:18:26,187
Don't worry, same thing happened for me.

150
00:18:26,937 --> 00:18:28,395
If we can't admit how we are feeling...

151
00:18:29,895 --> 00:18:31,520
