152
00:18:33,562 --> 00:18:35,020
You're a novitiate?

153
00:18:35,187 --> 00:18:36,187
Yeah.

154
00:18:36,353 --> 00:18:39,645
I just figured a little exploration
is healthy before the big day.

155
00:18:40,520 --> 00:18:42,853
I mean, I will be hiding this body...

156
00:18:43,645 --> 00:18:45,353
