at the orphanage that I grew up in.

163
00:19:16,312 --> 00:19:21,145
And we got pretty close because,
well, I was somewhat of a problem child.

164
00:19:21,645 --> 00:19:22,562
Wait.

165
00:19:22,728 --> 00:19:25,062
Wait, wait, wait. You were a problem child?

166
00:19:25,937 --> 00:19:26,937
Like how?

167
00:19:28,437 --> 00:19:29,728
I don't know. I guess...

168
00:19:30,645 --> 00:19:32,520
I mean, I used to get punished a lot.

169
00:19:35,062 --> 00:19:37,478
And how did they punish you?

170
00:19:38,103 --> 00:19:39,562
And where did you get these?

171
00:19:39,728 --> 00:19:40,562
Hey.

172
00:19:40,728 --> 00:19:43,187
