Do you know that?

173
00:19:45,437 --> 00:19:47,562
Well, would they beat you?

174
00:19:49,062 --> 00:19:50,312
Would they beat me?

175
00:19:51,728 --> 00:19:53,562
No, not really.

176
00:19:56,645 --> 00:19:59,270
I used to have a pretty active imagination.

177
00:20:01,437 --> 00:20:03,395
I'd get so convinced sometimes
that what I was seeing was real...

178
00:20:03,562 --> 00:20:05,437
that the sisters would need to...

179
00:20:07,603 --> 00:20:08,687
subdue me.

180
00:20:11,395 --> 00:20:14,937
But then Cardinal Lawrence
came to the orphanage...

181
00:20:15,103 --> 00:20:17,520
and he was really great, you know.

182
00:20:17,687 --> 00:20:20,312
He really helped me to see
that all that stuff was just in my head.

183
00:20:21,812 --> 00:20:23,812
Things got a lot better for me after that.

184
00:20:27,062 --> 00:20:28,228
For me...

185
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:30,687
