186
00:20:33,853 --> 00:20:35,312
I was 16.

187
00:20:36,353 --> 00:20:38,312
Just kicked out of the house.

188
00:20:39,353 --> 00:20:42,395
It was so cold that night,
and I didn't know what to do.

189
00:20:47,853 --> 00:20:48,853
And then...

190
00:20:51,020 --> 00:20:52,812
this warm wind came...

191
00:20:54,937 --> 00:20:56,270
out of nowhere.

192
00:21:00,020 --> 00:21:03,228
