as if His voice was all around me.

193
00:21:05,312 --> 00:21:06,687
Inside me even.

194
00:21:08,603 --> 00:21:09,978
So clearly.

195
00:21:11,770 --> 00:21:14,312
And He told me it didn't matter
if I had no earthly home...

196
00:21:14,478 --> 00:21:16,853
because my true home was with Him.

197
00:21:18,770 --> 00:21:20,853
And for the first time in my life...

198
00:21:22,103 --> 00:21:24,645
I felt like I belonged on this Earth.

199
00:21:30,978 --> 00:21:35,520
Yes, but even with the most handsome milkman
in town...

200
00:21:35,937 --> 00:21:39,270
