Sister.

359
00:35:48,978 --> 00:35:50,395
Sister, I need your help.

360
00:35:54,645 --> 00:35:56,728
Carlita, she's locked in a room.

361
00:35:57,228 --> 00:35:58,603
That's right.

362
00:35:58,937 --> 00:36:01,645
She bit Sister Romano just this morning...

363
00:36:02,645 --> 00:36:05,437
so she had to go to the bad room.

364
00:36:06,728 --> 00:36:09,895
Sister, why is there a bad room?

365
00:36:13,687 --> 00:36:17,312
Because some girls are bad.

366
00:36:39,103 --> 00:36:40,562
This room is suffocating.

367
00:36:42,187 --> 00:36:44,145
It's not meant to be pleasant.

368
00:36:44,770 --> 00:36:47,812
The things we do aren't always pleasant...

369
00:36:47,978 --> 00:36:50,103
but they are in the name of God.

370
00:36:54,728 --> 00:36:56,895
Do you wanna talk
about why they put you in that room?

371
00:37:01,562 --> 00:37:02,687
I'm bad.

372
00:37:04,312 --> 00:37:05,395
You're bad.

373
00:37:07,437 --> 00:37:09,103
Well, guess who else was bad.

374
00:37:10,812 --> 00:37:11,812
Who?

375
00:37:13,062 --> 00:37:14,062
You?

376
00:37:17,853 --> 00:37:18,853
Oh, yeah.

377
00:37:20,478 --> 00:37:21,728
But you know what?

378
00:37:23,770 --> 00:37:25,728
