408
00:43:06,728 --> 00:43:07,728
You all right?

409
00:43:11,853 --> 00:43:12,853
Yes?

410
00:43:26,728 --> 00:43:28,395
Here. Let's go for a walk.

411
00:43:33,603 --> 00:43:35,478
- Join the group.
- Oh, not today, girls.

412
00:43:35,645 --> 00:43:36,645
- Come on!
- Okay.

413
00:43:41,853 --> 00:43:43,520
No, no, no, not me.

414
00:43:44,603 --> 00:43:46,145
It's all right. It's okay.

