425
00:46:56,145 --> 00:46:57,645
You mentioned the name "Scianna."

426
00:46:58,062 --> 00:46:59,103
That's right.

427
00:47:06,812 --> 00:47:08,520
I assume you know these people.

428
00:47:10,187 --> 00:47:11,853
The priest is named Spiletto.

429
00:47:12,020 --> 00:47:13,312
He's a radical.

430
00:47:14,062 --> 00:47:15,312
Yes, I've seen him.

431
00:47:15,478 --> 00:47:16,478
Turn it over.

432
00:47:21,812 --> 00:47:23,562
The baby in this photo is Carlita?

433
00:47:23,728 --> 00:47:25,020
I believe so.

434
00:47:25,478 --> 00:47:27,062
And this is why she's in danger?

435
00:47:30,478 --> 00:47:31,770
I know these sisters.

436
00:47:31,937 --> 00:47:33,478
They're women of God.

437
00:47:33,645 --> 00:47:34,895
They belong to the Church.

438
00:47:35,062 --> 00:47:36,270
Listen to me, Margaret.

439
00:47:37,228 --> 00:47:40,145
The truth is there are two Churches.

440
00:47:40,728 --> 00:47:44,103
The one that follows the teachings of Christ,
the one that you and I are part of.

441
00:47:45,270 --> 00:47:46,270
And the other.

442
00:47:47,395 --> 00:47:51,395
The Church that will turn a blind eye
to torture, to rape.

443
00:47:51,895 --> 00:47:53,770
To commit murder in the name of God.

444
00:47:53,937 --> 00:47:55,687
All in the name of supreme power.

445
00:47:56,520 --> 00:47:59,020
What do you think that Church
is most frightened of?

446
00:48:00,687 --> 00:48:01,687
The Devil?

447
00:48:02,520 --> 00:48:04,020
Secularism.

448
00:48:05,187 --> 00:48:08,020
We are living in unprecedented times.

449
00:48:08,562 --> 00:48:11,020
Look at what's been occurring
in your very own generation.

450
00:48:11,853 --> 00:48:14,270
A culture that is outspoken, rebelling.

451
00:48:14,437 --> 00:48:16,020
Sometimes violently.

452
00:48:16,353 --> 00:48:19,437
People are turning away from the church
in droves.

453
00:48:20,062 --> 00:48:22,687
And, Margaret, you know as well as I do...

454
00:48:22,853 --> 00:48:24,937
that belief is power.

455
00:48:26,062 --> 00:48:28,687
Now, how do you control people
who no longer believe...

456
00:48:28,853 --> 00:48:31,187
in your stories of fire and brimstone?

457
00:48:32,062 --> 00:48:34,270
People who do not seem to fear?

458
00:48:35,603 --> 00:48:38,395
You create something to fear.

459
00:48:39,895 --> 00:48:43,312
This Church has maintained power
for generations.

460
00:48:43,520 --> 00:48:45,103
Thousands of years.

461
00:48:45,270 --> 00:48:47,645
And they will stop at nothing
to keep it that way.

462
00:48:51,437 --> 00:48:56,437
So, a small, but very powerful group
of priests and bishops...

463
00:48:57,603 --> 00:48:58,687
even higher...

464
00:49:00,270 --> 00:49:01,353
they decided...

465
00:49:02,103 --> 00:49:04,187
something drastic had to be done.

466
00:49:05,603 --> 00:49:06,895
These priests...

467
00:49:08,145 --> 00:49:11,562
...believe they can birth the Antichrist
and then control him.

468
00:49:12,895 --> 00:49:16,312
Allow him to bring his dark forces
to bear on the world...

469
00:49:16,478 --> 00:49:19,145
just enough
to drive people back to the Church.

470
00:49:19,312 --> 00:49:20,645
That's insane.

471
00:49:20,812 --> 00:49:22,895
Yes. Don't you see?

472
00:49:23,062 --> 00:49:25,437
If no one believes such a thing can exist...

473
00:49:26,103 --> 00:49:28,103
who will stand in their way?

474
00:49:31,478 --> 00:49:34,062
What does any of this
have to do with Carlita?

475
00:49:34,228 --> 00:49:35,770
I was excommunicated.

476
00:49:36,270 --> 00:49:38,520
My contacts within the Church
are very limited.

477
00:49:38,687 --> 00:49:40,728
That photo is all I have to go on.

478
00:49:42,895 --> 00:49:45,478
But I believe the baby girl in the picture...

479
00:49:46,145 --> 00:49:47,437
is to be the mother.

480
00:49:47,978 --> 00:49:49,687
The mother of what?

481
00:49:55,645 --> 00:49:57,270
Of the Antichrist?

482
00:49:57,770 --> 00:49:58,812
Yes.

483
00:50:00,853 --> 00:50:02,437
My God. You're crazy.

484
00:50:02,603 --> 00:50:03,645
Though if I am right...

485
00:50:03,812 --> 00:50:07,645
Carlita would have been born on the sixth day
of the sixth month at 6 a.m.

486
00:50:07,812 --> 00:50:08,895
666.

487
00:50:09,062 --> 00:50:11,562
It's the mark of the Devil
which she will have on her body.

488
00:50:11,895 --> 00:50:14,145
I don't understand
why you're telling me this.

489
00:50:14,312 --> 00:50:16,978
They're keeping her files at the orphanage.
Locked away.

490
00:50:17,562 --> 00:50:19,562
I need you to get them to me.

491
00:50:19,728 --> 00:50:22,478
I need to know how she was born.

492
00:50:23,187 --> 00:50:24,895
What do you mean, how she was born?

493
00:50:25,062 --> 00:50:26,187
Listen to me, Margaret.

494
00:50:26,353 --> 00:50:27,687
There is a beast they're mating.

495
00:50:28,103 --> 00:50:30,353
A jackal. That's the father.

496
00:50:30,687 --> 00:50:32,270
- I have to go now.
- No, no, Margaret.

497
00:50:33,395 --> 00:50:35,478
If Carlita is, in fact, the mother...

498
00:50:35,645 --> 00:50:38,937
the evil inside her
will do whatever it takes to stop us.

499
00:50:39,103 --> 00:50:41,312
We must destroy it at all costs.

500
00:50:41,478 --> 00:50:43,187
- Do you understand?
- No.

501
00:50:43,353 --> 00:50:45,603
Carlita is a little girl.

502
00:50:45,770 --> 00:50:47,020
And she is not pregnant.

503
00:50:47,187 --> 00:50:50,062
But we're not talking about a human child!

504
00:50:50,728 --> 00:50:52,062
It's almost June 6th.

505
00:50:52,228 --> 00:50:54,520
Look, we haven't a lot of time
and I need your help.

506
00:50:54,687 --> 00:50:56,103
No, you need a doctor.

507
00:50:56,270 --> 00:50:58,145
I'm sorry that I can't help you.

508
00:50:59,062 --> 00:51:00,520
Will you let go of my arm?

509
00:51:30,520 --> 00:51:31,645
Margaret.

510
00:51:31,812 --> 00:51:33,145
- Hi.
- How are you feeling?

511
00:51:34,312 --> 00:51:36,270
I need to talk to you about Carlita.

512
00:51:39,145 --> 00:51:41,937
Do you know anything about her history...

513
00:51:42,103 --> 00:51:44,978
or how she came to the orphanage?

514
00:51:46,437 --> 00:51:48,853
Not off the top of my head. Why?

515
00:51:49,812 --> 00:51:53,520
Do you know where I could find
that kind of information?

516
00:51:56,062 --> 00:51:59,687
I'm afraid this is not really my area,
you know?

517
00:52:58,978 --> 00:52:59,978
What?

518
00:53:01,478 --> 00:53:03,103
Why do you keep staring at me?

519
00:53:04,645 --> 00:53:05,645
I'm not.

520
00:53:14,603 --> 00:53:15,812
Will you come with me?

521
00:53:17,895 --> 00:53:18,812
Come on.

522
00:53:23,187 --> 00:53:25,020
I need to talk to you about something.

523
00:53:25,895 --> 00:53:26,937
But before I do...

524
00:53:27,478 --> 00:53:30,437
I just want you to know
that you can trust me, okay?

525
00:53:31,978 --> 00:53:33,062
Okay.

526
00:53:37,520 --> 00:53:40,895
Has anyone ever done anything to you...

527
00:53:41,937 --> 00:53:44,687
that might have scared you...

528
00:53:44,853 --> 00:53:46,187
or upset you?

529
00:53:52,853 --> 00:53:53,853
I don't know.

530
00:53:55,645 --> 00:53:57,062
What don't you know?

531
00:54:01,062 --> 00:54:02,687
Sometimes I get this...

532
00:54:03,978 --> 00:54:05,437
bad feelings.

533
00:54:08,645 --> 00:54:09,728
I see...

534
00:54:10,770 --> 00:54:12,395
I see things.

535
00:54:13,978 --> 00:54:18,520
And I can't tell if they're real or not.

536
00:54:20,312 --> 00:54:21,687
Listen to me.

537
00:54:23,103 --> 00:54:25,020
When I was younger...

538
00:54:26,270 --> 00:54:27,645
I used to have these...

539
00:54:28,520 --> 00:54:30,687
horrible visions.

540
00:54:31,437 --> 00:54:33,728
They were so terrible that I...

541
00:54:34,395 --> 00:54:37,103
convinced myself that they were real.

542
00:54:38,562 --> 00:54:42,853
But I learned that those thoughts...

543
00:54:43,728 --> 00:54:45,937
