629
01:02:25,437 --> 01:02:26,437
You ready?

630
01:02:39,562 --> 01:02:41,103
Oh, no, no.

631
01:02:42,520 --> 01:02:43,853
Oh, God.

632
01:02:45,103 --> 01:02:46,020
Oh, God.

633
01:02:46,187 --> 01:02:47,728
Oh, no, God.

634
01:05:50,270 --> 01:05:52,228
- Amen.
- Amen.

635
01:07:01,145 --> 01:07:02,312
Amen.

636
01:07:02,853 --> 01:07:04,478
Amen.

637
01:11:53,353 --> 01:11:54,353
Oh, God.

638
01:12:01,103 --> 01:12:02,228
Come on.

639
01:12:05,228 --> 01:12:06,312
Oh, God.

640
01:12:12,978 --> 01:12:13,978
Carlita.

641
01:12:14,145 --> 01:12:15,853
Come with me, Carlita.

642
01:12:27,228 --> 01:12:28,562
Okay, you go to the bed.

643
01:12:36,978 --> 01:12:39,728
