657
01:13:11,603 --> 01:13:13,228
- Remain calm!
- No, no, no!

658
01:13:32,103 --> 01:13:33,895
Please, please, I'm sorry.

659
01:13:34,395 --> 01:13:35,937
No, no, no!

660
01:13:36,437 --> 01:13:37,978
Not in there! Not in there! Not in there!

661
01:13:39,062 --> 01:13:41,020
No! No! No!

662
01:13:44,562 --> 01:13:46,312
Let me out!

663
01:13:46,937 --> 01:13:48,687
Please let me out!

664
01:13:50,520 --> 01:13:51,520
Please!

665
01:14:14,937 --> 01:14:16,312
Breathe. Breathe.

666
01:15:18,437 --> 01:15:21,812
...conviction: I am wanted.
I have a task in history.

667
01:15:23,228 --> 01:15:25,978
I am accepted. It is good that I exist.

668
01:15:26,645 --> 01:15:28,062
It is good to be a human being.

669
01:15:31,270 --> 01:15:33,603
Let every human heart experience your love.

670
01:16:25,187 --> 01:16:26,270
It's not real.

671
01:16:27,062 --> 01:16:30,437
It's not real. It's not real. It's not real.

672
01:16:30,645 --> 01:16:31,520
