674
01:17:40,062 --> 01:17:44,770
I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry.

675
01:17:59,812 --> 01:18:01,020
No!

676
01:18:01,312 --> 01:18:03,145
Margaret. We have to go.

677
01:18:03,312 --> 01:18:04,728
