01:19:05,562 --> 01:19:06,562
No, it's not safe.

700
01:19:06,728 --> 01:19:07,812
Not safe?

701
01:19:07,978 --> 01:19:09,478
She's the one
who's not safe right now, Gabriel.

702
01:19:09,645 --> 01:19:10,895
Margaret, after what just happened...

703
01:19:11,062 --> 01:19:13,312
they're not gonna let us
anywhere near that orphanage.

704
01:19:13,478 --> 01:19:14,687
Especially Carlita.

705
01:19:14,853 --> 01:19:15,895
He's right.

706
01:19:16,062 --> 01:19:18,937
It's only a matter of time
before they realize we've got these.

707
01:19:19,103 --> 01:19:21,312
And when they do, they will come for us.

708
01:19:21,478 --> 01:19:22,478
We have to help her.

709
01:19:22,645 --> 01:19:24,187
The only path forward...

710
01:19:24,353 --> 01:19:25,853
is to prove what they've done.

711
01:19:26,478 --> 01:19:28,353
Otherwise, no one will believe a word we say.

712
01:19:36,437 --> 01:19:38,187
There's so many of them.

713
01:19:38,353 --> 01:19:39,353
Yes.

714
01:19:40,062 --> 01:19:41,145
Too many.

715
01:19:42,687 --> 01:19:45,312
I had no idea they'd gone to such lengths.

716
01:19:51,770 --> 01:19:53,187
I don't understand.

717
01:19:53,812 --> 01:19:55,187
They need a male.

718
01:19:56,978 --> 01:19:58,687
They've only birthed females.

719
01:19:59,187 --> 01:20:01,270
They've all died except for Carlita.

720
01:20:01,437 --> 01:20:03,978
After all these years, so many failures...

721
01:20:06,853 --> 01:20:10,687
They believe the only way is for the beast
to mate with its own offspring.

722
01:20:30,728 --> 01:20:32,020
