723
01:20:32,437 --> 01:20:34,228
I told you,
it's the photo from Carlita's birth.

724
01:20:34,395 --> 01:20:35,395
No.

725
01:20:36,145 --> 01:20:37,145
This.

726
01:20:43,145 --> 01:20:44,145
It's the mark.

727
01:20:44,478 --> 01:20:46,520
