with the mark on its scalp.

739
01:21:20,645 --> 01:21:22,062
We must have missed something.

740
01:21:22,228 --> 01:21:23,228
Right?

741
01:21:46,478 --> 01:21:47,312
Where is it?

742
01:21:48,103 --> 01:21:49,562
{\an8}Why do they all look like this?

743
01:21:50,520 --> 01:21:53,228
{\an8}The father. He's not human.

744
01:22:27,562 --> 01:22:28,687
It's her.

745
01:22:33,020 --> 01:22:34,687
There was another survivor.

746
01:22:37,353 --> 01:22:38,353
A sister?

747
01:22:39,020 --> 01:22:40,562
Did you know about this?

748
01:22:40,728 --> 01:22:41,728
No.

749
01:22:41,978 --> 01:22:43,312
They must have kept it hidden away.

750
01:23:10,770 --> 01:23:15,562
Look for the mark.

751
01:23:18,187 --> 01:23:19,645
How did he know?

752
01:23:22,520 --> 01:23:24,020
He knew where it was.

753
01:26:42,228 --> 01:26:43,728
Margaret, Margaret. Hush.

754
01:26:44,353 --> 01:26:46,978
Margaret. Margaret. Margaret.

755
01:26:48,312 --> 01:26:49,728
Just let me have a look.

756
01:26:50,687 --> 01:26:51,687
Let me look.

757
01:27:19,353 --> 01:27:21,020
Somebody say something.

758
01:27:23,187 --> 01:27:24,562
