767
01:27:51,312 --> 01:27:52,937
- Don't you touch me!
- ...you can't just leave.

768
01:27:53,103 --> 01:27:55,437
You touch me again, I'll fucking kill you!

769
01:28:07,353 --> 01:28:08,562
I'm so sorry.

770
