778
01:28:42,978 --> 01:28:44,770
I need it out of me now.

779
01:28:54,395 --> 01:28:55,395
Margaret...

780
01:28:56,145 --> 01:28:57,353
you all right?

781
01:28:57,895 --> 01:29:00,187
This doctor knows what he's doing?

782
01:29:01,187 --> 01:29:02,978
He's experienced, yes.

783
01:29:30,978 --> 01:29:32,603
Wait. Stop. What are you doing?

784
01:29:32,937 --> 01:29:33,895
Don't stop.

785
01:29:34,062 --> 01:29:35,853
Make like you're heading for the main road...

786
01:29:36,020 --> 01:29:37,520
and then turn off before the arch.

787
01:29:50,145 --> 01:29:50,978
Margaret.

788
01:29:56,270 --> 01:29:57,895
What's happening to me?

789
01:33:41,645 --> 01:33:42,937
Hello?

790
01:33:43,812 --> 01:33:44,937
Hello?

791
01:33:46,562 --> 01:33:48,478
Can anyone hear me?

792
01:33:48,645 --> 01:33:49,645
Yes.

793
01:33:50,645 --> 01:33:51,728
I can hear.

794
01:33:55,853 --> 01:33:58,937
I can't tell if this is real or not.

795
01:33:59,395 --> 01:34:03,353
This is very real, Margaret.

796
01:34:04,520 --> 01:34:06,062
Can you untie me?

797
01:34:06,895 --> 01:34:08,062
Soon.

798
01:34:09,145 --> 01:34:11,812
Soon it will be all over, I promise.

799
01:34:16,103 --> 01:34:17,103
No.

800
01:34:17,270 --> 01:34:19,437
No, no.

801
01:34:19,603 --> 01:34:21,395
You don't have to be afraid.

802
01:34:22,812 --> 01:34:25,353
I won't let anything bad happen to you.

803
01:34:28,895 --> 01:34:30,478
I've watched over you...

804
01:34:31,520 --> 01:34:33,103
since you were a little girl.

805
01:34:36,020 --> 01:34:39,520
The very first moment we met,
do you remember what I said to you?

806
01:34:41,103 --> 01:34:45,395
That you, Margaret, were the bravest girl
I'd ever known.

807
01:34:46,520 --> 01:34:49,812
Now you know how special you are to me.

808
01:34:50,020 --> 01:34:51,020
To us.

809
01:34:53,478 --> 01:34:57,937
The baby you're about to bear
will redeem the Church.

810
01:34:58,103 --> 01:35:01,312
