819
01:35:35,853 --> 01:35:37,812
I... No.

820
01:35:54,895 --> 01:35:56,103
There.

821
01:35:56,270 --> 01:35:57,687
You're ready now.

822
01:35:58,395 --> 01:36:00,228
Please know that I love you.

823
01:36:04,728 --> 01:36:06,562
I'll be right here.

824
01:37:17,978 --> 01:37:19,020
Stay down.

825
01:37:45,687 --> 01:37:46,687
No, no.

826
01:37:48,728 --> 01:37:50,228
No, no. Please.

827
01:38:02,478 --> 01:38:04,020
Please, please, please.

828
01:38:04,562 --> 01:38:05,770
No.

829
01:38:07,812 --> 01:38:09,103
No, no, no.

830
01:38:10,478 --> 01:38:11,478
No, please.

831
01:38:15,520 --> 01:38:16,520
Please.

832
01:38:16,687 --> 01:38:17,687
Please.

833
01:38:50,103 --> 01:38:51,562
Help me, please.

834
01:38:52,853 --> 01:38:54,770
Please help me. Please.

835
01:38:54,937 --> 01:38:56,312
Please, untie me.

836
01:38:57,562 --> 01:38:59,603
Please untie me, I'm in pain.

837
01:39:03,103 --> 01:39:05,478
I'm in pain. Please.

838
01:39:07,853 --> 01:39:08,853
Help.

839
01:39:10,770 --> 01:39:12,270
Help me, please.

840
01:39:12,437 --> 01:39:13,770
Please help me.

841
01:39:15,603 --> 01:39:16,603
Help me.

842
01:39:17,395 --> 01:39:19,687
Help. I'm in pain.

843
01:40:21,687 --> 01:40:23,395
What is it? A boy or girl?

844
01:40:33,062 --> 01:40:34,520
There are two.

845
01:40:35,728 --> 01:40:36,853
A girl...

846
01:40:40,895 --> 01:40:42,228
And the other?

847
01:40:43,437 --> 01:40:44,478
A boy!

848
01:40:49,437 --> 01:40:50,687
We have him.

849
01:41:53,770 --> 01:41:54,770
Help.

850
01:41:55,103 --> 01:41:57,770
- Help. Help.
- Of course.

851
01:41:57,937 --> 01:41:58,937
Of course, my dear.

852
01:41:59,103 --> 01:42:00,853
- I'm in pain.
- Of course.

853
01:42:05,895 --> 01:42:07,478
Can I hold him?

854
01:42:11,937 --> 01:42:13,228
You're sure?

855
01:42:15,978 --> 01:42:18,353
I'm his mother. I'm his mother.

856
01:42:20,187 --> 01:42:21,603
Bring him here.

857
01:42:24,395 --> 01:42:25,603
She's right.

858
01:42:26,270 --> 01:42:31,062
It is important for a child
to bond with its mother.

859
01:42:36,520 --> 01:42:41,062
We all need the comfort of our mothers
in the beginning.

860
01:42:41,770 --> 01:42:43,020
Don't we?

861
01:42:47,978 --> 01:42:50,187
You did so well, my child.

862
01:42:57,187 --> 01:42:59,853
You are doing God's work.

863
01:43:00,020 --> 01:43:02,603
He would be so proud of you.

864
01:43:02,770 --> 01:43:05,103
Can't you hear Him telling you?

865
01:43:05,270 --> 01:43:07,312
Don't you hear His voice?

866
01:43:12,437 --> 01:43:13,478
No.

867
01:43:17,020 --> 01:43:18,937
No, I only hear my own.

868
01:43:22,937 --> 01:43:24,187
No!

869
01:43:52,187 --> 01:43:53,145
Margaret.

870
01:43:54,937 --> 01:43:56,270
Stop this.

871
01:43:58,853 --> 01:44:02,228
Margaret, give me the baby.

872
01:44:03,937 --> 01:44:05,978
Just give me the baby.

873
01:44:16,937 --> 01:44:17,812
No!

874
01:44:41,687 --> 01:44:43,103
Burn everything.

875
01:44:43,270 --> 01:44:44,937
Leave them both to die.

876
01:46:11,770 --> 01:46:12,770
It's okay.

877
01:48:03,145 --> 01:48:05,020
The man you are looking for.

878
01:48:05,270 --> 01:48:07,353
The US Ambassador to Rome.

879
01:48:08,312 --> 01:48:10,020
He will be the new father.

880
01:48:12,062 --> 01:48:15,145
<i>He and his wife will suffer a tragic loss...</i>

881
01:48:15,645 --> 01:48:16,978
<i>and be in need of a child.</i>

882
01:48:20,728 --> 01:48:23,145
<i>The boy will inherit their privilege...</i>

883
01:48:23,312 --> 01:48:24,395
<i>and power.</i>

884
01:48:26,895 --> 01:48:29,978
<i>Soon, his darkness will spread...</i>

885
01:48:31,312 --> 01:48:34,312
<i>and the world shall be saved.</i>

886
01:49:10,437 --> 01:49:12,562
Baby, you're supposed to eat them.

887
01:49:12,728 --> 01:49:13,895
You're supposed to eat them like...

888
01:49:14,645 --> 01:49:15,645
Like that.

889
01:49:19,103 --> 01:49:20,395
What are you doing?

890
01:49:22,562 --> 01:49:23,478
Come here.

891
01:49:28,312 --> 01:49:29,728
No, no, no. Here.

892
01:49:30,728 --> 01:49:31,728
This.

893
01:49:31,895 --> 01:49:32,978
No, not this.

894
01:49:33,145 --> 01:49:34,145
You want one?

895
01:49:35,812 --> 01:49:36,812
You want it?

896
01:49:38,520 --> 01:49:39,728
Give it to Mama. Give it to Mama.

897
01:49:39,895 --> 01:49:40,895
Give it to Mama.

898
01:50:02,895 --> 01:50:04,437
I'm so sorry, Margaret.

899
01:50:07,353 --> 01:50:09,020
I tried just to leave you be.

900
01:50:12,895 --> 01:50:14,270
You need to go.

901
01:50:15,103 --> 01:50:16,312
Now.

902
01:50:18,520 --> 01:50:19,895
I came to warn you.

903
01:50:21,270 --> 01:50:22,645
They know you're alive.

904
01:50:23,853 --> 01:50:26,395
You weren't supposed to survive.
None of you were.

905
01:50:26,853 --> 01:50:28,312
Especially the girl.

906
01:50:31,270 --> 01:50:33,020
She'll be important, Margaret.

907
01:50:35,812 --> 01:50:37,395
I just want to be left alone.

908
01:50:39,187 --> 01:50:40,228
I know.

909
01:50:42,228 --> 01:50:43,520
But they will come for you.

910
01:51:02,020 --> 01:51:03,645
They've even given it a name.

911
01:51:05,478 --> 01:51:06,853
Your son.

912
01:51:09,270 --> 01:51:10,353
Damien.
